flowchart TD
  START{what is the<br/>pressure?} -->|CPU or memory<br/>rises with traffic| HPA["<b>HPA</b><br/>add/remove replicas<br/>on CPU/memory<br/>(this module)"]
  START -->|requests are bursty<br/>or idle for long stretches| KN["<b>Serverless</b><br/>scale to zero<br/>(cross-ref Serverless)"]
  START -->|work is driven by a<br/>queue / event backlog| KEDA["<b>KEDA</b><br/>scale on queue depth<br/>(cross-ref Jobs / Eventing)"]
  START -->|one pod is chronically<br/>over- or under-provisioned| VPA["<b>VPA</b><br/>right-size requests<br/>(concept only)"]
  classDef pick fill:#e6f4ea,stroke:#137333,color:#0d652d;
  classDef other fill:#f3f3f3,stroke:#888,color:#333;
  class HPA pick;
  class KN,KEDA,VPA other;
